So, mark your calendars and prepare for a day of insightful learning and professional growth. Let's shape the future together-because the sky's the limit!

Are you ready to 𝐒𝐓𝐀𝐑𝐓-𝐔𝐏, 𝐒𝐄𝐑𝐕𝐄, 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐒𝐎𝐀𝐑 into the dynamic world of hospitality and tourism? 

We invite you to be part of an exciting event on:
🗓️𝐒𝐞𝐩𝐭𝐞𝐦𝐛𝐞𝐫 𝟐𝟒, 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓 (Wednesday)
⏰ 1:00 PM-5:00 PM
📍 𝐌𝐢𝐧𝐢 𝐀𝐮𝐝𝐢𝐭𝐨𝐫𝐢𝐮𝐦, 𝐅𝐄𝐔𝐭𝐮𝐫𝐞 𝐂𝐞𝐧𝐭𝐞𝐫 𝐁𝐮𝐢𝐥𝐝𝐢𝐧𝐠, 𝐅𝐄𝐔 𝐌𝐚𝐧𝐢𝐥𝐚

This year’s theme, 𝐒𝐓𝐀𝐑𝐓-𝐔𝐏, 𝐒𝐄𝐑𝐕𝐄, 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐒𝐎𝐀𝐑, “𝐂𝐡𝐚𝐦𝐩𝐢𝐨𝐧𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐅𝐮𝐭𝐮𝐫𝐞 𝐨𝐟 𝐇𝐨𝐬𝐩𝐢𝐭𝐚𝐥𝐢𝐭𝐲 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐰𝐢𝐭𝐡 𝐚 𝐆𝐥𝐨𝐛𝐚𝐥 𝐌𝐢𝐧𝐝𝐬𝐞𝐭”, is your chance to explore how innovation can shape our vibrant industries, brought to you by 𝐊𝐚𝐰𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐏𝐫𝐨𝐝𝐮𝐜𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧𝐬! 

Whether you’re an aspiring Entrepreneur, HRM and Tourism Students, this event is designed to inspire and equip you with the tools you need to thrive!

So, mark your calendars and prepare for a day of insightful learning and professional growth. Let's shape the future together-because the sky's the limit! 

𝐑𝐞𝐠𝐢𝐬𝐭𝐞𝐫 𝐧𝐨𝐰 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐛𝐞 𝐩𝐚𝐫𝐭 𝐨𝐟 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐞𝐱𝐜𝐢𝐭𝐞𝐦𝐞𝐧𝐭! Don’t miss out on this incredible opportunity!
